    "name": "Gnome Expedition",
    "steam_appid": 3136930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gnome Expedition is a short but intense fantasy horror game where you must collect ingredients for your Gnome-Style Stew, while being chased by a demonic knight that is about 10x your size. You navigate through a maze-like map while you roam the dirt trenches in between the woods. Enter a world of retro, PS2 inspired graphics in a fantastical grand forest that progressively grows more haunted and gruesome. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running is enhanced by sprinting, but sprint wisely, as you are limited with a stamina bar.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power Ups</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mushrooms: Collect mushrooms that significantly boost your stamina.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enchanted Rose: Each level has one rose, which can provide you 5 seconds of invincibility.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power ups are stored in your inventory. Use them wisely to help evade difficult situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maps</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be given a map for each progressing variant of the forest. Use it to help you navigate to the end of the forest, which guarantee that you collect all the ingredients you need from your checklist. There are many tricks and turns in the woods; if you're lost, make sure to use the totem poles and other landmarks to help you find your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a student project, if you enjoy, please leave a review!</p>",
